# 🔐 Secure Credential Generator (Java)

A GUI-based password generator built using Java Swing and AWT, designed to create strong, random, and customizable passwords.
This tool ensures security by generating credentials with combinations of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and special characters.

🚀 Features

Generate secure and random passwords.

Options to include:

✅ Uppercase letters

✅ Lowercase letters

✅ Numbers

✅ Symbols

Customizable password length.

Simple and intuitive Graphical User Interface (GUI).

Lightweight and easy to run.

🛠️ Tech Stack

Java (Core)

Swing (GUI components)

AWT (Abstract Window Toolkit for UI elements)

java.util.Random (randomization utilities)

